#: ../../boot_options.rst:2
msgid "Boot options"
msgstr "Dewisiadau cychwyn"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:4
msgid ""
"Some graphics cards and motherboards don't work well with the open-source "
"drivers present in Linux Mint by default."
msgstr ""
"Nid yw rhai cardiau graffigau a mamfyrddau yn gweithio'n dda gyda'r gyrwyr "
"cod agored sydd yn Linux Mint."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:7
msgid "Compatibility mode"
msgstr "Modd cydnawsedd"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:9
msgid ""
"The easiest option is to select ``compatibility mode`` from the USB stick "
"(or DVD) boot menu."
msgstr ""
"Y ffordd hawsaf yw i ddewis y \"modd cydnawsedd\" o ddewislen cychwyn cof "
"bach USB neu DVD."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:15
msgid "Grub menu (EFI mode)"
msgstr "Dewislen grub (modd EFI)"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:21
msgid "Isolinux menu (BIOS mode)"
msgstr "Dewislen isolinux (Modd BIOS)"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:23
msgid "If that doesn't work, you can try the ``nomodeset`` boot option."
msgstr "Os nad yw hynny'n gweithio, gallwch drio'r dewis cychwyn \"nomodeset"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:26
msgid "Nomodeset boot option"
msgstr "Dewis cychwyn nomodesel"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:28
msgid ""
"In EFI mode, highlight the ``Start Linux Mint`` option and press :kbd:`e` to "
"modify the boot options."
msgstr ""
"Yn y modd EFI, amlygwch y dewis \"Start Linux Mint\" a pwyso :kbd:`e` i "
"newid y dewisiadau cychwyn."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:34
msgid ""
"Replace ``quiet splash`` with ``nomodeset`` and press :kbd:`F10` to boot."
msgstr ""
"Newidiwch y ``quiet splash`` i ``nomodeset`` a phwyso :kbd:`F10` i gychwyn."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:36
msgid ""
"In BIOS mode, highlight ``Start Linux Mint`` and press :kbd:`Tab` to modify "
"the boot options."
msgstr ""
"Yn y modd BIOS, amlygu ``Start Linux Mint`` ac agor :kbd:`Tab` i newid y "
"dewisiadau cychwyn."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:42
msgid ""
"Replace ``quiet splash`` with ``nomodeset`` and press :kbd:`Enter` to boot."
msgstr ""
"Newidiwch ``quiet splash`` i ``nomodeset`` a phwyso :kbd:`Enter` i gychwyn."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:45
msgid ""
"Repeat this operation post-install in your grub boot menu and read "
":doc:`drivers` to install additional drivers."
msgstr ""
"Gwnewch y weithred hon eto ar ôl y gosod yn newislen cychwyn Grub a darllen "
":doc:'drivers' er mwyn gosod gyrwyr ychwanegol."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:48
msgid "Other boot options"
msgstr "Dewisiadau cychwyn eraill"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:50
msgid "If you still cannot boot try one of the following solutions:"
msgstr "Os nad oes modd cychwyn o hyd, rhowch gynnig ar y canlynol:"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:52
msgid "Try ``nouveau.noaccel=1`` instead of ``nomodeset``."
msgstr "``nouveau.noaccel=1`` yn lle ``nomodeset``."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:53
msgid ""
"After the installation, use :menuselection:`Advanced Options --> Recovery "
"mode` from the boot menu and choose ``resume``."
msgstr ""
"Ar ôl gosod, defnyddiwch :menuselection:`Advanced Options --> Recovery mode` "
"o'r ddewislen cychwyn a dewis  ``resume``."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:56
msgid "Install an older release"
msgstr "Gosod fersiwn hŷn"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:58
msgid ""
"If your computer has compatibility issues with the latest Linux Mint "
"release, install a previous release from the same Linux Mint series."
msgstr ""
"Os nad yw eich cyfrifiadur yn gydnaws â'r fersiwn diweddaraf o Linux Mint, "
"beth am osod fersiwn blaenorol o Linux Mint?"

#: ../../boot_options.rst:60
msgid ""
"For instance, if you can't install Linux Mint 18.3 (which comes with a 4.10 "
"kernel), install Linux Mint 18 (which comes with a 4.4 kernel) and upgrade "
"to 18.3."
msgstr ""
"Er enghraifft, os nad oes modd i chi osod Linux Mint 18.3 (sy'n cynnwys "
"cnewyllyn 4.10), beth am osod 18 (sydd â chnewyllyn 4.4) a diweddaru i 18.3."

#: ../../boot_options.rst:63
msgid ""
"The first release in each series uses an LTS (Long Term Support) kernel. "
"Upgrading from this release to the latest one in the series does not change "
"your kernel."
msgstr ""
"Mae fersiwn cyntaf pob cyfres yn defnyddio cnewyllyn LTS (Long Term "
"Support). Nid yw diweddaru o'r diweddaraf yn y gyfres yn newid eich "
"cnewyllyn."

#: ../../boot.rst:2
msgid "Boot Linux Mint"
msgstr "Cychwyn Linux Mint"

#: ../../boot.rst:4
msgid ""
"Now that you have Linux Mint on a USB stick (or DVD) boot the computer from "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Nawr bod gennych Linux Mint ar gof bach USB (neu DVD) gallwch gychwyn eich "
"cyfrifiadur drwyddo."

#: ../../boot.rst:6
msgid "Insert your USB stick (or DVD) into the computer."
msgstr "Mewnosodwch eich cof bach USB (neu DVD) i'r cyfrifiadur."

#: ../../boot.rst:8 ../../drivers.rst:23 ../../efi.rst:61 ../../oem.rst:21
msgid "Restart the computer."
msgstr "Ailgychwynnch y cyfrifiadur"

#: ../../boot.rst:10
msgid ""
"Before your computer boots your current operating system (Windows, Mac, "
"Linux) you should see your `BIOS <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BIOS>`_ "
"loading screen. Check the screen or your computer's documentation to know "
"which key to press and instruct your computer to boot on USB (or DVD)."
msgstr ""
"Cyn bod y cyfrifiadur yn cychwyn eich system weithredu gyfredol (Windows, "
"Mac, Linux) dylech weld sgrin llwytho eich `BIOS "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BIOS>`. Gwiriwch y sgrin neu ddogfennaeth "
"eich cyfrifiadur er mwyn gwybod pa fysell i'w phwyso a dweud wrth eich "
"cyfrifiadur i gychwyn o'r cof bach (neu DVD)."

#: ../../boot.rst:13
msgid ""
"Most BIOS have a special key you can press to select the boot device and all "
"of them have a special key to enter the BIOS configuration screen (from "
"which you can define the boot order). Depending on the BIOS, these special "
"keys can be :kbd:`Escape`, :kbd:`F1`, :kbd:`F2`, :kbd:`F8`, :kbd:`F10`, "
":kbd:`F11`, :kbd:`F12`, or :kbd:`Delete`. That information is usually "
"briefly written on the screen during the boot sequence."
msgstr ""
"Mae gan y rhan fwyaf o BIOS fysell arbennig i'w phwyso i ddewis cychwyn y "
"ddyfais ohoni ac mae gan bob un fysell arbennig i fynd i sgrin ffurfweddu'r "
"BIOS  (yn lle mae modd diffinio'r drefn cychwyn). Yn ddibynnol ar y BIOS, "
"gall y bysellau arbennig hyn fod yn :kbd:`Escape`, :kbd:`F1`, :kbd:`F2`, "
":kbd:`F8`, :kbd:`F10`, :kbd:`F11`, :kbd:`F12`, neu :kbd:`Delete`. Fel rheol "
"mae'r wybodaeth yma ar gael yn sydyn wrth gychwyn y cyfrifiadur."

#: ../../boot.rst:16
msgid ""
"On Macs, keep your finger pressed on the :kbd:`Alt` or :kbd:`Option` key "
"after hearing the boot sound."
msgstr ""
"Ar y Mac, cadwch eich bys i bwyso ar fysellau :kbd:`Alt` neu :kbd:`Option` "
"ar ôl clywed y sain cychwyn."

#: ../../boot.rst:18
msgid ""
"The Linux Mint ISO can be booted both in EFI or BIOS mode. In EFI mode it "
"shows a grub menu. In BIOS mode it shows an isolinux menu."
msgstr ""
"Gellir lwytho ISO Linux Mint ym modd EFI neu BIOS. Ym modd EFI mae'n dangos "
"dewislen grub. Ym modd BIOS mae'n dangos dewislen isolinux."

#: ../../boot.rst:24
msgid "The isolinux menu in BIOS mode"
msgstr "Dewislen isolinux ym modd BIOS"

#: ../../boot.rst:30
msgid "The grub menu in EFI mode"
msgstr "Dewislen grub ym modd EFI"

#: ../../boot.rst:32
msgid ""
"From one of these menu, press :kbd:`Enter` to start Linux Mint from your USB "
"stick (or DVD)."
msgstr ""
"O un o'r dewislenni hyn, pwyswch :kbd:`Enter` i gychwyn Linux Mint o'ch cof "
"bach USB (neu DVD)."

#: ../../burn.rst:2
msgid "Create the bootable media"
msgstr "Crëwch gyfrwng i fedru llwytho'r system"

#: ../../burn.rst:4
msgid "The easiest way to install Linux Mint is with a USB stick."
msgstr "Defnyddio cof bach USB yw'r ffordd mwyaf cyfleus i osod Linux Mint."

#: ../../burn.rst:6
msgid "If you cannot boot from USB, you can use a blank DVD."
msgstr "Os nad yw'n bosib llwytho o USB, mae modd defnyddio DVD gwag."

#: ../../burn.rst:9
msgid "How to make a bootable USB stick"
msgstr "Sut i greu cof bach USB cychwynadwy"

#: ../../burn.rst:12
msgid "In Linux Mint"
msgstr "Yn Linux Mint"

#: ../../burn.rst:14
msgid ""
"Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Make Bootable USB "
"Stick`, or launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Accessories --> USB Image Writer`."
msgstr ""
"De-gliciwch y ffeil ISO a dewis :menuselection: `Creu Cof Bach USB "
"Cychwynadwy`, neu gychwyn :menuselection:` Dewislen -> Ategolion -> Awdur "
"Delwedd USB`."

#: ../../burn.rst:20
msgid "Select your USB device and click :guilabel:`Write`."
msgstr "Dewiswch eich dyfais USB a chlicio :guilabel:`Ysgrifennu`."

#: ../../burn.rst:23
msgid "In Windows, Mac OS, or other Linux distributions"
msgstr "Yn Windows, Mac OS, neu ddosbarthiadau Linux eraill"

#: ../../burn.rst:25
msgid ""
"Download `Etcher <https://www.balena.io/etcher/>`_, install it and run it."
msgstr ""
"Llwythwch `Etcher <https://www.balena.io/etcher/>` i lawr, ei osod a'i redeg."

#: ../../burn.rst:31
msgid "Using Etcher"
msgstr "Defnyddio Etcher"

#: ../../burn.rst:33
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select image` and select your ISO file."
msgstr "Cliciwch :guilabel:`Dewiswch ddelwedd` a dewis eich ffeil ISO."

#: ../../burn.rst:35
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Select drive` and select your USB stick."
msgstr "Cliciwch :guilabel:`Dewiswch yriant` a dewis eich cof bach USB."

#: ../../burn.rst:37
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Flash!`."
msgstr "Cliciwch :guilabel:`Fflachio!`."

#: ../../burn.rst:41
msgid "How to make a bootable DVD"
msgstr "Sut i wneud DVD cychwyn"

#: ../../burn.rst:43
msgid "Optical discs are slow and burning to disc is prone to errors."
msgstr ""
"Mae disgiau optegol yn araf ac mae llosgi i ddisg yn dueddol o greu "
"camgymeriadau."

#: ../../burn.rst:46
msgid "To prevent issues, burn at the lowest possible speed."
msgstr "Er mwyn atal problemau, llosgwch ar y cyflymder isaf posibl."

#: ../../burn.rst:49
msgid ""
"Burn the content of the ISO onto the DVD, not the ISO file itself. When "
"finished, your DVD should contain directories such as ``boot`` and "
"``casper``, it shouldn't be an empty DVD containing an .iso file."
msgstr ""
"Llosgwch gynnwys yr ISO ar y DVD, nid y ffeil ISO ei hun. Ar ôl gorffen, "
"dylai eich DVD gynnwys cyfeiriaduron fel ``boot`` a ``casper``, ni ddylai "
"fod yn DVD gwag sy'n cynnwys ffeil .iso."

#: ../../burn.rst:52
msgid "In Linux"
msgstr "Yn Linux"

#: ../../burn.rst:53
msgid "Install and use ``xfburn``."
msgstr "Gosod a defnyddio ``xfburn``."

#: ../../burn.rst:56
msgid "In Windows"
msgstr "Yn Windows"

#: ../../burn.rst:57
msgid "Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Burn disk image`."
msgstr ""
"De-gliciwch y ffeil ISO a dewis :menuselection: `Llosgi delwedd disg`."

#: ../../burn.rst:59
msgid ""
"To make sure the ISO was burned without any errors, select "
":menuselection:`Verify disc after burning`."
msgstr ""
"Er mwyn sicrhau bod yr ISO wedi'i losgi heb unrhyw wallau, dewiswch "
":menuselection: `Gwirio disg ar ôl ei losgi`."

#: ../../burn.rst:62
msgid "In Mac OS"
msgstr "Yn Mac OS"

#: ../../burn.rst:63
msgid ""
"Right-click the ISO file and select :menuselection:`Burn Disk Image to Disc`."
msgstr ""
"De-gliciwch y ffeil ISO a dewis :menuselection: `Llosgi delwedd disg`."

#: ../../choose.rst:2
msgid "Choose the right edition"
msgstr "Dewiswch y rhifyn cywir"

#: ../../choose.rst:4
msgid ""
"You can download Linux Mint from the `Linux Mint website "
"<https://linuxmint.com/download.php>`_."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch lwytho Linux Mint i lawr o wefan `Linux Mint "
"<https://linuxmint.com/download.php>` _."

#: ../../choose.rst:6
msgid ""
"Read below to choose which edition and architecture are right for you."
msgstr ""
"Darllenwch isod i ddewis pa fersiwn a phensaernïaeth sy'n iawn i chi."

#: ../../choose.rst:9
msgid "Cinnamon, MATE or Xfce?"
msgstr "Cinnamon, MATE neu Xfce?"

#: ../../choose.rst:11
msgid ""
"Linux Mint comes in 3 different flavours, each featuring a different desktop "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"Mae Linux Mint yn dod mewn 3 math gwahanol, pob un yn cynnwys amgylchedd "
"bwrdd gwaith gwahanol."

#: ../../choose.rst:14 ../../choose.rst:26
msgid "Cinnamon"
msgstr "Cinnamon"

#: ../../choose.rst:14
msgid "The most modern, innovative and full-featured desktop"
msgstr "Y bwrdd gwaith mwyaf modern, arloesol a llawn nodweddion"

#: ../../choose.rst:15 ../../choose.rst:35
msgid "MATE"
msgstr "MATE"

#: ../../choose.rst:15
msgid "A more traditional, and faster desktop"
msgstr "Bwrdd gwaith mwy traddiodiadol a chynflymach."

#: ../../choose.rst:16 ../../choose.rst:44
msgid "Xfce"
msgstr "XFce"

#: ../../choose.rst:16
msgid "The most lightweight desktop"
msgstr "Y bwrdd gwaith mwyaf ysgafn"

#: ../../choose.rst:19
msgid ""
"The most popular version of Linux Mint is the Cinnamon edition. Cinnamon is "
"primarily developed for and by Linux Mint. It is slick, beautiful, and full "
"of new features."
msgstr ""
"Y fersiwn fwyaf poblogaidd o Linux Mint yw'r un Cinnamon. Mae Cinnamon yn "
"cael ei ddatblygu'n bennaf ar gyfer a chan Linux Mint. Mae'n slic, hardd, ac "
"yn llawn nodweddion newydd."

#: ../../choose.rst:28
msgid ""
"Linux Mint is also involved in the development of MATE, a classic desktop "
"environment which is the continuation of GNOME 2, Linux Mint's default "
"desktop between 2006 and 2011. Although it misses a few features and its "
"development is slower than Cinnamon's, MATE uses less resources and can run "
"faster on older computers."
msgstr ""
"Mae Linux mint hefyd yn ymwneud â datblygiad MATE, amgylchedd bwrdd gwaith "
"clasurol sy'n barhad o GNOME2, bwrdd gwaith rhagosodedig Linux Mint rhwng "
"2006 a 2011. Er ei fod yn brin o rai nodweddion ac mae ei ddatblygiad yn "
"arafach na Cinnamon, mae MATE yn defnyddio llai o adnoddau ac yn gallu "
"rhedeg yn gynt ar gyfrifiaduron hŷn."

#: ../../choose.rst:37
msgid ""
"Xfce is a lightweight desktop environment. It doesn't support as many "
"features as Cinnamon or MATE, but it's extremely stable and very light on "
"resource usage."
msgstr ""
"Mae Xfce yn amgylchedd bwrdd gwaith ysgafn. Nid yw'n cefnogi cymaint o "
"nodweddion â Cinnamon neu MATE, ond mae'n hynod sefydlog ac yn ysgafn iawn "
"ar y defnydd o adnoddau."

#: ../../choose.rst:46
msgid ""
"Of course, all three desktops are great and Linux Mint is extremely proud of "
"each edition. Although there are more features and better support in some "
"editions than others, and some do run faster and use less resources than "
"others, they're all great alternatives and choosing the right edition is "
"largely a matter of taste."
msgstr ""
"Wrth gwrs, mae'r tri bwrdd gwaith yn wych ac mae Linux Mint yn hynod falch o "
"bob un. Er bod mwy o nodweddion a gwell cefnogaeth mewn rhai fersiynau nag "
"eraill, a bod rhai yn rhedeg yn gyflymach ac yn defnyddio llai o adnoddau "
"nag eraill, maen nhw i gyd yn ddewisiadau amgen gwych ac mae dewis y fersiwn "
"cywir yn fater o chwaeth i raddau helaeth."

#: ../../choose.rst:48
msgid ""
"Other than their features and performance, Cinnamon, MATE and Xfce also "
"represent three different desktop environments, with different menus, "
"different panels and configuration tools. The right one for you is the one "
"where you feel at home."
msgstr ""
"Heblaw am eu nodweddion a'u perfformiad, mae Cinnamon, MATE a Xfce hefyd yn "
"cynrychioli tri amgylchedd bwrdd gwaith gwahanol, gyda gwahanol ddewislenni, "
"gwahanol baneli ac offer ffurfweddu. Yr un iawn i chi yw'r un lle rydych "
"chi'n teimlo'n gartrefol."

#: ../../choose.rst:50
msgid ""
"If you are unsure which desktop to choose start with the Cinnamon edition. "
"Try them all eventually when you have the time. All three of them have their "
"own audience within the Linux Mint community and they're all very popular."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych chi'n ansicr pa fwrdd gwaith i'w ddewis, dechreuwch gyda'r fersiwn "
"Cinnamon. Rhowch gynnig arnyn nhw i gyd yn y pen draw pan fydd gennych chi'r "
"amser. Mae gan y tri ohonyn nhw eu cynulleidfa eu hunain yng nghymuned Linux "
"Mint ac maen nhw i gyd yn boblogaidd iawn."

#: ../../choose.rst:54
msgid "32-bit or 64-bit?"
msgstr "32-did neu 64-did?"

#: ../../choose.rst:56
msgid "From version 20 onward, only 64-bit is available."
msgstr "O fersiwn 20 ymlaen dim ond 64-did sydd ar gael."

#: ../../choose.rst:58
msgid ""
"The 32-bit ISO images on prior versions are provided for compatibility with "
"older computers. 32-bit processors are extremely rare nowadays and most "
"computers are able to run in 64-bit. If your computer was manufactured after "
"2007, you probably have a 64-bit processor."
msgstr ""
"Mae'r delweddau ISO 32-did  wedi eu darparu ar gyfer cydnawsedd â "
"chyfrifiaduron hŷn. Mae proseswyr 32-did yn brin iawn y dyddiau hyn ac mae'r "
"mwyafrif o gyfrifiaduron yn gallu rhedeg o fewn 64-did. Os cafodd eich "
"cyfrifiadur ei gynhyrchu ar ôl 2007, mae'n debyg bod gennych brosesydd 64-"
"did."

#: ../../choose.rst:60
msgid ""
"If you have an old computer and you are unsure whether or not it can run in "
"64-bit, read `X86 Chronology "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86#Chronology>`_."
msgstr ""
"Os oes gennych hen gyfrifiadur a'ch bod yn ansicr a all redeg mewn 64-bit ai "
"peidio, darllenwch `X86 Chronology "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/X86#Chronology>`_."

#: ../../choose.rst:63
msgid ""
"You can try to boot Linux Mint 64-bit on your computer. If it isn't "
"compatible, nothing bad will happen. You will just get an error message."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch geisio cychwyn Linux Mint 64-did ar eich cyfrifiadur. Os nad yw'n "
"gydnaws, ni fydd unrhyw beth drwg yn digwydd. Fe gewch chi neges gwall yn "
"unig."

#: ../../choose.rst:66
msgid ""
"If you cannot boot or install Linux Mint because your hardware is too recent "
"and is not properly detected see the `Edge ISO Images <https://linuxmint-"
"user-guide.readthedocs.io/en/latest/edge.html>`_ chapter in the Linux Mint "
"User Guide for an alternative ISO."
msgstr ""
"Os nad ydych yn gallu cychwyn na gosod Linux Mint oherwydd fod eich "
"caledwedd yn rhy ddiweddar ac heb ei ganfod yn gywir darllenwch y bennod "
"`Edge ISO Images <https://linuxmint-user-"
"guide.readthedocs.io/en/latest/edge.html>`_ yn y Linux Mint User Guide am "
"ISO amgen."

#: ../../codecs.rst:2
msgid "Multimedia codecs"
msgstr "Codec amlgyfrwng"

#: ../../codecs.rst:4
msgid "Some multimedia content requires additional codecs to be installed."
msgstr ""
"Mae rhywfaint o gynnwys amlgyfrwng yn gofyn am osod codecau ychwanegol."

#: ../../codecs.rst:7
msgid ""
"If you were online when installing Linux Mint and you ticked the option to "
"install these codecs, they are already installed."
msgstr ""
"Os oeddech chi ar-lein wrth osod Linux Mint a'ch bod wedi ticio'r opsiwn i "
"osod y codecau hyn, maen nhw eisoes wedi'u gosod."

#: ../../codecs.rst:9
msgid ""
"Launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Sound & Video --> Install Multimedia Codecs`."
msgstr ""
"Cychwyn :menuselection: `Dewislen -> Sain a Fideo -> Gosod Codecs "
"Amlgyfrwng`."

#: ../../codecs.rst:14
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Install`."
msgstr "Clicio :guilabel:`Gosod`."

#: ../../codecs.rst:16
msgid ""
"Enter your password and wait for the codecs to be installed on your computer."
msgstr ""
"Rhowch eich cyfrinair ac aros i'r codecau gael eu gosod ar eich cyfrifiadur."

#: ../../drivers.rst:2
msgid "Hardware drivers"
msgstr "Gyrwyr caledwedd"

#: ../../drivers.rst:4
msgid ""
"One of the first things to do after installing Linux Mint is to check for "
"available hardware drivers."
msgstr ""
"Un o'r pethau cyntaf i'w wneud ar ôl gosod Linux Mint yw gwirio am y gyrwyr "
"caledwedd sydd ar gael."

#: ../../drivers.rst:6
msgid "Launch :menuselection:`Menu --> Administration --> Driver Manager`."
msgstr ""
"Cychwyn :menuselection: `Dewislen --> Gweinyddiaeth -> Rheolwr Gyrwyr`."

#: ../../drivers.rst:13
msgid ""
"If you are offline, the Driver Manager will complain that it cannot connect "
"to the Internet."
msgstr ""
"Os ydych yn all-lein, bydd y Rheolwr Gyrwyr yn cwyno na all gysylltu â'r "
"Rhyngrwyd."

#: ../../drivers.rst:19
msgid ""
"Insert your bootable Linux Mint USB stick (or DVD), wait for it to be "
"mounted, and click :guilabel:`OK`."
msgstr ""
"Mewnosodwch eich cof bach USB (neu DVD) Linux Mint cychwynadwy, arhoswch "
"iddi gael ei gosod, a chlicio :guilabel: `Iawn`."

#: ../../drivers.rst:21
msgid ""
"Tick the appropriate checkboxes to select the available drivers and click "
":guilabel:`Apply Changes`."
msgstr ""
"Ticiwch y blychau gwirio priodol i ddewis y gyrwyr sydd ar gael a chlicio "
":guilabel: `Gosod y Newidiadau`."

#: ../../efi.rst:2
msgid "EFI"
msgstr "EFI"

#: ../../efi.rst:5
msgid "SecureBoot"
msgstr "SecureBoot"

#: ../../efi.rst:7
